<title>USA: Schuller changes name, ups shr authorization.</title>
<headline>Schuller changes name, ups shr authorization.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1997-05-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Schuller Corp said on Monday its shareholders approved changing the company's name back to Johns Manville Corp, with the new company symbol of JM.N , effective today.</p>
<p>At the company's annual meeting, shareholders also approved an increase of the authorized shares of common stock by 125 million shares, Schuller said.</p>
<p>Johns Manville makes insulation and building products.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
